        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "The 'ladder': one rook cuts off the 7th rank, the other delivers mate on the 8th. 1.Rb7 forces the black king onto the back rank (Kd8 or Kf8 — both lose), and 2.Ra8# completes the staircase. Two rooks corner the king without any king help needed, which is why this mate is so quick.",
          "target": "'阶梯'：一个车封锁第7横线，另一个在第8横线将杀。1.Rb7 迫使黑王回到底线（Kd8 或 Kf8——两者皆输），2.Ra8# 完成阶梯。两个车无需王的帮助即可将王逼入角落，这就是为什么这个将杀如此迅速。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "With your king in front of a 7th-rank pawn (not a- or h-file) and your rook free, build a 'bridge' on the 4th rank (Rc4!), then march your king out behind it. The defending rook eventually runs out of useful checks and the pawn promotes.",
          "target": "当你的王位于第7横线兵前（非 a 或 h 线兵），且你的车自由时，在第4横线搭建一座'桥'（Rc4!），然后让王从后面走出来。防守方的车最终会耗尽有用的将军，兵得以升变。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Defender's rook attacks the a-pawn from the side along the 6th rank, the defender's king cuts the long side. The white king can never both shield the pawn and escape the side checks — drawn.",
          "target": "防守方的车从第6横线侧翼攻击 a 兵，防守方的王切断长边。白王永远无法同时保护兵并避开侧翼将军——和棋。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Study chess in your vault. Embed positions, study openings and endgames, browse World Championship games, annotate PGNs, and explore Lichess opening statistics.",
          "target": "在您的保险库中学习国际象棋。嵌入局面，学习开局和残局，浏览世界冠军赛对局，注释 PGN，并探索 Lichess 开局统计。"
        },
        {
